import Vue from 'vue'
import Vuex from 'vuex'

Vue.use(Vuex)
import home from './home'
import search from './search'
import detail from './detail'
import shopcart from './shopcart'
import user from './user'
import trade from './trade'
import pay from './pay'


export default new Vuex.Store({
    modules:{
        home,
        search,
        detail,
        shopcart,
        user,
        trade,
        pay
    }
})
